      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Exhibiting consistent mechanical integrity and a refined interior, it delivers a sophisticated and reliable driving experience. Every component has been thoroughly inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for performance and safety. A distinguished choice for those seeking a vehicle that balances executive presence with proven durability.",
