      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car! I\u2019ve honestly loved every mile in this beauty, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride that still looks great in the driveway. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will enjoy it as much as I have. It\u2019s ready to hit the road today, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by for a test drive!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
