    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW M2 is a stunning example of a driver-focused machine, finished in iconic Long Beach Blue Metallic. The exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster, showing only the minor stone chips on the front fascia expected of a well-loved road car. Inside, the cabin remains a premium environment; the black Dakota leather seats are supple with minimal bolster wear, and the carbon fiber interior trim is free of scratches. Every electronic component, from the navigation system to the heated seats, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is bone-dry and pulls with exhilarating force, backed by a comprehensive service history that proves its mechanical health. The car sits on original 19-inch wheels with fresh performance rubber, offering a tight, responsive handling profile. This is a turn-key enthusiast vehicle that balances exhilarating performance with the reliability of a well-documented maintenance life.",
